CreateGeoMatchSet.name: CreateGeoMatchSet
CreateGeoMatchSet.description:
Creates a GeoMatchSet, which you use to specify which web requests you want to allow
                                                or block based on the country that the requests originate from.

CreateIPSet.name: CreateIPSet
CreateIPSet.description:
Creates an IPSet, which you use to specify which web requests you want to allow or
                                                block based on the IP addresses that the requests originate from.

CreateRateBasedRule.name: CreateRateBasedRule
CreateRateBasedRule.description:
Creates a RateBasedRule, which contains a RateLimit specifying the maximum number
                                                of requests that AWS WAF allows from a specified IP address in a five-minute period.

CreateRegexMatchSet.name: CreateRegexMatchSet
CreateRegexMatchSet.description:
Creates a RegexMatchSet, which you use to specify which web requests you want to allow
                                                or block based on the regex patterns you specified in a RegexPatternSet.

CreateRegexPatternSet.name: CreateRegexPatternSet
CreateRegexPatternSet.description:
Creates a RegexPatternSet, which you use to specify the regular expression (regex)
                                                pattern that you want AWS WAF to search for.

CreateRule.name: CreateRule
CreateRule.description:
Creates a Rule, which contains the IPSet objects, ByteMatchSet objects, and other
                                                predicates that identify the requests that you want to block.

CreateRuleGroup.name: CreateRuleGroup
CreateRuleGroup.description:
Creates a RuleGroup. A rule group is a collection of predefined rules that you add
                                                to a WebACL.

CreateSizeConstraintSet.name: CreateSizeConstraintSet
CreateSizeConstraintSet.description:
Creates a SizeConstraintSet, which you use to identify the part of a web request that
                                                you want to check for length.

CreateSqlInjectionMatchSet.name: CreateSqlInjectionMatchSet
CreateSqlInjectionMatchSet.description:
Creates a SqlInjectionMatchSet, which you use to allow, block, or count requests that
                                                contain snippets of SQL code in a specified part of web requests.

CreateWebACL.name: CreateWebACL
CreateWebACL.description:
Creates a WebACL, which contains the Rules that identify the CloudFront web requests
                                                that you want to allow, block, or count.

CreateWebACLMigrationStack.name: CreateWebACLMigrationStack
CreateWebACLMigrationStack.description:
Create and store a CloudFormation tempalte that creates an equivalent WAF v2 WebACL
                                                from the given WAF Classic WebACL in the given S3 bucket.

CreateXssMatchSet.name: CreateXssMatchSet
CreateXssMatchSet.description:
Creates an XssMatchSet, which you use to allow, block, or count requests that contain
                                                cross-site scripting attacks in the specified part of web requests.

DeleteLoggingConfiguration.name: DeleteLoggingConfiguration
DeleteLoggingConfiguration.description: Permanently deletes the LoggingConfiguration from the specified web ACL.

DeletePermissionPolicy.name: DeletePermissionPolicy
DeletePermissionPolicy.description: Permanently deletes an IAM policy from the specified RuleGroup.

GetByteMatchSet.name: GetByteMatchSet
GetByteMatchSet.description: Returns the ByteMatchSet specified by ByteMatchSetId.

GetChangeToken.name: GetChangeToken
GetChangeToken.description:
When you want to create, update, or delete AWS WAF objects, get a change token and
                                                include the change token in the create, update, or delete request.

GetChangeTokenStatus.name: GetChangeTokenStatus
GetChangeTokenStatus.description: Returns the status of a ChangeToken that you got by calling GetChangeToken.

GetGeoMatchSet.name: GetGeoMatchSet
GetGeoMatchSet.description: Returns the GeoMatchSet specified by GeoMatchSetId.

GetIPSet.name: GetIPSet
GetIPSet.description: Returns the IPSet that is specified by IPSetId.

GetLoggingConfiguration.name: GetLoggingConfiguration
GetLoggingConfiguration.description: Returns the LoggingConfiguration for the specified web ACL.

GetPermissionPolicy.name: GetPermissionPolicy
GetPermissionPolicy.description: Returns the IAM policy attached to the RuleGroup.

GetRateBasedRule.name: GetRateBasedRule
GetRateBasedRule.description:
Returns the RateBasedRule that is specified by the RuleId that you included in the
                                                GetRateBasedRule request.

GetRateBasedRuleManagedKeys.name: GetRateBasedRuleManagedKeys
GetRateBasedRuleManagedKeys.description:
Returns an array of IP addresses currently being blocked by the RateBasedRule that
                                                is specified by the RuleId.

GetRegexMatchSet.name: GetRegexMatchSet
GetRegexMatchSet.description: Returns the RegexMatchSet specified by RegexMatchSetId.

GetRegexPatternSet.name: GetRegexPatternSet
GetRegexPatternSet.description: Returns the RegexPatternSet specified by RegexPatternSetId.

GetRule.name: GetRule
GetRule.description:
Returns the Rule that is specified by the RuleId that you included in the GetRule
                                                request.

GetRuleGroup.name: GetRuleGroup
GetRuleGroup.description:
Returns the RuleGroup that is specified by the RuleGroupId that you included in the
                                                GetRuleGroup request.

GetSampledRequests.name: GetSampledRequests
GetSampledRequests.description:
Gets detailed information about a specified number of requests--a sample--that AWS
                                                WAF randomly selects from among the first 5,000 requests that your AWS resource received
                                                during a time range that you choose.

GetSizeConstraintSet.name: GetSizeConstraintSet
GetSizeConstraintSet.description: Returns the SizeConstraintSet specified by SizeConstraintSetId.

GetSqlInjectionMatchSet.name: GetSqlInjectionMatchSet
GetSqlInjectionMatchSet.description: Returns the SqlInjectionMatchSet that is specified by SqlInjectionMatchSetId.

GetWebACL.name: GetWebACL
GetWebACL.description: Returns the WebACL that is specified by WebACLId.

GetXssMatchSet.name: GetXssMatchSet
GetXssMatchSet.description: Returns the XssMatchSet that is specified by XssMatchSetId.

ListActivatedRulesInRuleGroup.name: ListActivatedRulesInRuleGroup
ListActivatedRulesInRuleGroup.description: Returns an array of ActivatedRule objects.

ListByteMatchSets.name: ListByteMatchSets
ListByteMatchSets.description: Returns an array of ByteMatchSetSummary objects.

ListGeoMatchSets.name: ListGeoMatchSets
ListGeoMatchSets.description: Returns an array of GeoMatchSetSummary objects.

ListIPSets.name: ListIPSets
ListIPSets.description: Returns an array of IPSetSummary objects in the response.

ListLoggingConfigurations.name: ListLoggingConfigurations
ListLoggingConfigurations.description: Returns an array of LoggingConfiguration objects.

ListRateBasedRules.name: ListRateBasedRules
ListRateBasedRules.description: Returns an array of RuleSummary objects.

ListRegexMatchSets.name: ListRegexMatchSets
ListRegexMatchSets.description: Returns an array of RegexMatchSetSummary objects.

ListRegexPatternSets.name: ListRegexPatternSets
ListRegexPatternSets.description: Returns an array of RegexPatternSetSummary objects.

ListRuleGroups.name: ListRuleGroups
ListRuleGroups.description: Returns an array of RuleGroup objects.

ListRules.name: ListRules
ListRules.description: Returns an array of RuleSummary objects.

ListSizeConstraintSets.name: ListSizeConstraintSets
ListSizeConstraintSets.description: Returns an array of SizeConstraintSetSummary objects.

ListSqlInjectionMatchSets.name: ListSqlInjectionMatchSets
ListSqlInjectionMatchSets.description: Returns an array of SqlInjectionMatchSet objects.

ListSubscribedRuleGroups.name: ListSubscribedRuleGroups
ListSubscribedRuleGroups.description: Returns an array of RuleGroup objects that you are subscribed to.

ListTagsForResource.name: ListTagsForResource
ListTagsForResource.description: Lists the Tags for a given resource.

ListWebACLs.name: ListWebACLs
ListWebACLs.description: Returns an array of WebACLSummary objects in the response.

ListXssMatchSets.name: ListXssMatchSets
ListXssMatchSets.description: Returns an array of XssMatchSet objects.

PutLoggingConfiguration.name: PutLoggingConfiguration
PutLoggingConfiguration.description: Associates a LoggingConfiguration with a specified web ACL.

PutPermissionPolicy.name: PutPermissionPolicy
PutPermissionPolicy.description:
Attaches a IAM policy to the specified resource. The only supported use for this action
                                                is to share a RuleGroup across accounts.

TagResource.name: TagResource
TagResource.description: Adds a Tag to a given resource.

UntagResource.name: UntagResource
UntagResource.description: Removes a Tag from a given resource.

UpdateByteMatchSet.name: UpdateByteMatchSet
UpdateByteMatchSet.description: Inserts or deletes ByteMatchTuple objects (filters) in a ByteMatchSet.

UpdateGeoMatchSet.name: UpdateGeoMatchSet
UpdateGeoMatchSet.description: Inserts or deletes GeoMatchConstraint objects in a GeoMatchSet.

UpdateIPSet.name: UpdateIPSet
UpdateIPSet.description: Inserts or deletes IPSetDescriptor objects in an IPSet.

UpdateRateBasedRule.name: UpdateRateBasedRule
UpdateRateBasedRule.description: Inserts or deletes Predicate objects in a rule and updates the RateLimit in the rule.

UpdateRegexMatchSet.name: UpdateRegexMatchSet
UpdateRegexMatchSet.description: Inserts or deletes RegexMatchTuple objects (filters) in a RegexMatchSet.

UpdateRegexPatternSet.name: UpdateRegexPatternSet
UpdateRegexPatternSet.description: Inserts or deletes RegexPatternStrings in a RegexPatternSet.

UpdateRule.name: UpdateRule
UpdateRule.description: Inserts or deletes Predicate objects in a Rule.

UpdateRuleGroup.name: UpdateRuleGroup
UpdateRuleGroup.description: Inserts or deletes ActivatedRule objects in a RuleGroup.

UpdateSizeConstraintSet.name: UpdateSizeConstraintSet
UpdateSizeConstraintSet.description: Inserts or deletes SizeConstraint objects (filters) in a SizeConstraintSet.

UpdateSqlInjectionMatchSet.name: UpdateSqlInjectionMatchSet
UpdateSqlInjectionMatchSet.description: Inserts or deletes SqlInjectionMatchTuple objects (filters) in a SqlInjectionMatchSet.

UpdateWebACL.name: UpdateWebACL
UpdateWebACL.description: Inserts or deletes ActivatedRule objects in a WebACL.

UpdateXssMatchSet.name: UpdateXssMatchSet
UpdateXssMatchSet.description: Inserts or deletes XssMatchTuple objects (filters) in an XssMatchSet.
